      "id": "PopularPost287053",
      "post_content": "Buuut~ While it's true that Pestilence remains the source of the damage, unless they activate it all at once they can just let the 1 damages resolve one by one until you cast this spell, at which point they can do the rest of the activations in response, letting you block a grand total of 1 damage with this spell.",
